dbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Mai 15, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104eiq1665702549359.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eiq1665702549359.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eiq1665702549359.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"eiq1665702549359\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the directory where the application's configuration files are located.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eiq1665702549359__section_w6729ab1b5b1_w6730ab1b5_w6731ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eiq1665702549359__p_d147728e1_d147729e1_d147730e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/adm=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">AdmDirectory</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eiq1665702549359__section_w6732ab1b5b3_w6733ab1b5_w6734ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d294642e61\">\n                  \n Use with\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eiq1665702549359__p_d147734e1_d147735e1_d147736e1\">All Uniface applications.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eiq1665702549359__section_w6735ab1b5b5_w6736ab1b5_w6737ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d294642e70\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eiq1665702549359__p_d147740e1_d147741e1_d147742e1\">Uniface has multiple <span class=\"ph filepath\">adm</span> directories containing configuration files—in <span class=\"ph filepath\">common</span> and in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">uniface</span> product directory. To ensure that the correct configuration files are used, Uniface applications, including the Uniface IDE, must be started with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/adm</span> switch to set the correct context.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eiq1665702549359__p_d147743e1_d147744e1_d147745e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/adm</span> should be specified before <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/asn</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/ini</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iil1665702549278.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/asn</a><p>Specify the assignment file used by the application.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exv1665702549479.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/ini</a><p>Specify the initialization file or GUI resource file used by the application.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527157\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527157\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/adm Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Mai 15, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify the directory where the application's configuration files are located. /adm= AdmDirectory Use with All Uniface applications. Description Uniface has multiple adm directories containing configuration files—in common and in the uniface product directory. To ensure that the correct configuration files are used, Uniface applications, including the Uniface IDE, must be started with the /adm switch to set the correct context. /adm should be specified before /asn or /ini Related Links /asn Specify the assignment file used by the application. /ini Specify the initialization file or GUI resource file used by the application. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}